snippet.title: Quiet Maple - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Quiet Maple is an atmospheric experience about maple syrup creation in Quebec's cold.

This game was made in 30 days by myself.

I'm releasing a new game every single month and this one is the first in the serie, you can follow the development of the next ones and even get them for free by supporting me on patreon.

Quiet Maple :
Patreon :https://www.patreon.com/Tayf
Twitter : https://twitter.com/TayNayaF
